    Enum representing different medical specialties and their associated charges.
    Technician
    The Technician class extends the Provider class.

    The Timeslot class represents a time slot in a scheduling system, allowing for the creation of time slots corresponding to specific hours and minutes in a 12-slot format, spanning from 9:00 AM to 4:30 PM.
